; Open/Close Account Beancount File
; Testing open and close directives

2013-01-01 open Assets:US:BofA:Checking USD
2013-01-01 open Assets:US:BofA:Savings USD
2013-01-01 open Liabilities:CreditCard:CapitalOne USD
2013-01-01 open Income:US:Salary
2013-01-01 open Expenses:Restaurant
2013-01-01 open Expenses:Groceries

; First use of checking
2013-01-15 * "Initial deposit"
  Assets:US:BofA:Checking  2000.00 USD
  Income:US:Salary  -2000.00 USD

; Using credit card
2013-02-01 * "Restaurant dinner"
  Liabilities:CreditCard:CapitalOne  -75.00 USD
  Expenses:Restaurant  75.00 USD

; Close credit card after fraud
2014-11-28 close Liabilities:CreditCard:CapitalOne

; New credit card account opened later
2015-01-01 open Liabilities:CreditCard:Chase USD

; Open with currency constraint
2015-01-01 open Assets:Investments Brokerage USD

; Open with booking method
2015-01-01 open Assets:Investments:Old  USD "STRICT"

; Open with multiple currencies
2015-01-01 open Assets:MultiCurrency USD, EUR, CAD

; Open with NONE booking method for flexible matching
2015-01-01 open Liabilities:CreditCard:Flexible  USD, EUR "NONE"

; Close an old account
2015-06-30 close Assets:Investments:Old